    nav
    main
        h1 Robe
        h2 ODM for MongoDB using ES6 generators

        +code('bash').
          $ npm install --save robe

        section#intro
          :markdown
            **Robe** wraps around [monk](https://github.com/Automattic/monk) to provide a 
            simple yet effective ODM library for MongoDB. 

            Overview:

            * Object-oriented extensibility.
            * Use documents or raw data, your choice.
            * Before and after Hooks.
            * Stream results using cursors.
            * Optional schema validation.
            * Full access to Mongo filtering and updating modifiers.

